There a bad interaction between a exim config and postgrey, this patch ports the
new method of parsing IP addresses from postgrey from the current git repo,
which should prevent the crash from happening.

This patch should also be used to fix the problem in stretch

This patch fixes the Debian bug https://bugs.debian.org/867201

